content:
But what moves me even more about your response is that,
even though you didn't witness it firsthand,
you believed in me without hesitation.{开心}

Much more effective than counting sheep - I'll be sound asleep in no time.
The only downside is that I keep forgetting to turn off my computer...
It's quite energy-consuming, isn't it? {开心}

I have never...{短暂停}
{想象中}<color=#d3b037>{Pnickname}</color> said as such,
I believe I understand now.

Thanks, friend!
I've found my path forward! I'm off to train harder!
<size=30>I won't lose to papa, hmph...</size>{思考中}

Hmm, I see...{短暂停}
Yes, it was truly wonderful,
I remember our chance encounter, right there on the sunset shore.

I see, you're just like Glenn,
you both know I'm not that kind of person.{开心}
Actually, I went to find Glenn early, but the shop wasn't open.

...Oh.{短暂停}
<color=#695c3a>...This is quite excessive indeed.</color>
Right, sixteen boxes were damaged indeed.

Hmm... Next time, {短暂停}
if I make an effort to stay focused,
perhaps I'll be able to better appreciate the allure of fishing?

Don't worry, my head is quite well-cushioned,
I absolutely won't hurt myself! {短暂停}
Though, perhaps I should inflate my posterior a bit before bedtime?

Oh my,
This conversation has naturally turned into an invitation~
Perhaps... would you like to gaze at the celestial river with me tonight? {微笑}

It was that yellow one with my portrait carved on it{短暂停}
Oh, perhaps it was indigo blue...
Hmm, now which one did I lose exactly...

{思考}
Perhaps we'll accidentally succeed,
And reproduce even more mantis shrimp?

No, that's not quite right.{短暂停}
Starting to feel puzzled, aren't you?{微笑}
Very well, I shall reveal the answer.

Such a fascinating experience,
I simply had to share it with you!
Different from what you imagined, isn't it?{坏笑}

I hope that in every joyful moment to come,
we'll always be together.
My dearest friend!{微笑}

It's transformed into an entirely new "car-planting" game! {短暂停}
What's with that expression of yours?
Oh dear, Esassani isn't standing right behind me, is she?

Talking with you was definitely the right choice,
you've opened up new perspectives for me.{短暂停}
<size=30>Though I do wish my professor had trusted me more back then...</size>{思考中}
